  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101480/extras/09b2177db103ca7e0229e033bb1747b6.avif?t=1668623699\" width=600 height=70 /></span><br>You need to get home safely after a wild night out. On the way, you will encounter many obstacles that will make your journey difficult. The game includes two game modes: Arcade & Endurance.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101480/extras/0901ada7fb142bb9cfd3e2b014c6abb2.poster.avif?t=1668623699\" width=600 height=399 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101480/extras/0901ada7fb142bb9cfd3e2b014c6abb2.webm?t=1668623699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101480/extras/dde532607ba7db04b32043f6121dbd65.avif?t=1668623699\" width=600 height=70 /></span><br>The maneuverability of the game is based on momentum, so be careful with your inputs.<br>The game also features jumping, which requires perfect timing and coordination.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101480/extras/e01aa384f052f6b2ffe7a723866a83bb.poster.avif?t=1668623699\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101480/extras/e01aa384f052f6b2ffe7a723866a83bb.webm?t=1668623699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101480/extras/e01aa384f052f6b2ffe7a723866a83bb.mp4?t=1668623699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101480/extras/ac7b08d184bdfe9025b76e004a962856.webp?t=1668623699\" width=600 height=45 /></span><br>The slightest mistake will make you tumble down so be careful with your movements!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101480/extras/e00058077c41faf1e165016131b3f4d1.poster.avif?t=1668623699\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101480/extras/e00058077c41faf1e165016131b3f4d1.webm?t=1668623699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101480/extras/e00058077c41faf1e165016131b3f4d1.mp4?t=1668623699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
